*  rm .doit.db
*  nikola clean
*  nikola check --clean-files



Adding a new page

.. code-block:: sh
  
  nikola new_page
  
Enter a title for your page. It will be the name of your page too.

If you entered index as title then this will be your index page

It will be saved in pages/

.. code-block:: sh

  nikola new_page  pages/course/cpp/index.txt
  nikola new_page --title="first test file"  pages/test1.rst
  nikola new_page --title="index courses"  pages/course/index.rst
  nikola new_page --title="cpp"  pages/course/cpp.rst

